memberdef.name: SCHEMA
memberdef.initializer: = new Schema( required(1, "longCol", Types.LongType.get()), required(2, "intCol", Types.IntegerType.get()), required(3, "floatCol", Types.FloatType.get()), optional(4, "doubleCol", Types.DoubleType.get()), optional(5, "decimalCol", Types.DecimalType.of(20, 5)), optional(6, "dateCol", Types.DateType.get()), optional(7, "timestampCol", Types.TimestampType.withZone()), optional(8, "stringCol", Types.StringType.get()))

detaileddescription.para: A benchmark that evaluates the performance of reading Parquet data with a flat schema using Iceberg and Spark Parquet readers.

To run this benchmark for spark-3.3: ./gradlew -DsparkVersions=3.3 :iceberg-spark:iceberg-spark-3.3_2.12:jmh -PjmhIncludeRegex=SparkParquetReadersFlatDataBenchmark -PjmhOutputPath=benchmark/spark-parquet-readers-flat-data-benchmark-result.txt
A benchmark that evaluates the performance of reading Parquet data with a flat schema using Iceberg and Spark Parquet readers.

To run this benchmark for spark-3.5: ./gradlew -DsparkVersions=3.5 :iceberg-spark:iceberg-spark-3.5_2.12:jmh -PjmhIncludeRegex=SparkParquetReadersFlatDataBenchmark -PjmhOutputPath=benchmark/spark-parquet-readers-flat-data-benchmark-result.txt
